text = "when you lay hands on what-
ever passes for a videogame
in your heart, there is the
question: what is this that
has touched me back so? the
thing is briefly alive with-
in your machine. there's no
way to describe the feeling
so we choose whatever works
even if it's incorrect. our
solipsistic society thinks,
but forgets whatever cannot
be digested into a smoothed
pebble. thus a game is made
into our action, our story,
the game is anything except
for what it is.

a game is not a memory, and
it is not a place, nor is a
game action, or rules.

i cannot describe the infi-
nite, but every work beyond
our flimsy \"soul\" and brief
but very real response lies
in some material plane, one
we reside within as well. a
thing much like a videogame
has a finite but very large
surface, one that we cannot
grasp or perceive totally.

you, however, are   ."
label_settings = ExtResource("7_ryvow")

