[node name="Room10Labels" type="Node2D" parent="Game/V" unique_id=1959791617]
position = Vector2(245, 5)

[node name="Label" type="Label" parent="Game/V/Room10Labels" unique_id=1969856371]
offset_left = 95.0
offset_top = 5.0
offset_right = 235.0
offset_bottom = 175.0
text = "when a videogame changes we
must know that it only does
so within strict bounds, of
definition known to the one
who created it.

so we know and at times try
to forget. i reject totally
any arguments to illusion.

know what you make.

create with intention.

if you fear that work, then
promptly deal with it, and,
fearlessly, proceed.

if you do not know what you
make, then take the time it
takes to understand it, and
then, familiar with what it
is, proceed.

if it cannot be understood,
then it is not art. but too
it must be possible to mis-
understand it. again if you
fear misunderstanding, take
the time necessary. come to
terms with an understanding
and its impossibility.

your own, too. you're   ."
label_settings = ExtResource("7_ryvow")

